---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Company Companion — LeadFair"
  description="A private AI trained on your company's knowledge. Your team gets instant answers about policies, procedures, and processes — without interrupting you."
  headline="Your Company's Brain, On Tap"
  subheadline="A private AI trained on everything your team needs to know — policies, procedures, pricing rules, how-to guides. Your employees get instant answers without interrupting you."
  accentColor="primary"
>
  <!-- What It Does -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dots opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-4">What the Company Companion Does</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 text-lg">It's like giving every employee direct access to the owner's brain — without the owner being there.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Answers Team Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Employees ask and get instant answers about company policies, procedures, pricing, and schedules. No more "let me ask the owner."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Onboards New Hires</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">New employees learn the ropes faster. The companion walks them through processes, explains how things work, and answers questions from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Knows Your Processes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">How do we handle a refund? What's the pricing for a group lesson? What's the cancellation policy? Your companion knows it all because you taught it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Protects Your Time</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Stop being the bottleneck for every question. Your team gets what they need, and you get to focus on actually running the business.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Stays Up to Date</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">When policies change, we update the companion. Your team always has access to the latest information — no outdated handbooks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Private & Secure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">This is an internal tool. Your company knowledge stays private — it's not exposed to customers or the public. Only your team has access.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-blue-green">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">How We Set It Up</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl shrink-0 animate-float">
            <span class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Document Your Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-lg">We work with you to capture your company knowledge — policies, procedures, FAQs, processes, pricing rules, and anything else your team needs to know.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl shrink-0 animate-float-delay">
            <span class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Build & Train</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-lg">We build the AI with your knowledge base and set up access for your team. Everyone gets the same consistent, accurate answers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl shrink-0 animate-float-slow">
            <span class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Deploy & Evolve</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed text-lg">Your team starts using it immediately. As your business changes, we update the companion to keep it current — no stale information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-warm">
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Business owners tired of answering the same questions from staff</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Companies with processes that are hard to remember or keep straight</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Teams that need consistent answers — not "it depends on who you ask"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-10 h-10 rounded-lg shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text font-medium">Owners who want to step back without the business falling apart</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
